#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>meinproc6</command> converts DocBook files to &HTML;."
msgstr "<command>meinproc6</command> pretvori DocBook datoteke v &HTML;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic Options"
msgstr "Splošne možnosti"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-h</option><option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<option>-h</option><option>--help</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show help about options."
msgstr "Pokaži pomoč o možnostih."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-v</option><option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<option>-v</option><option>--version</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version information."
msgstr "Prikaži informacije o različici."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Options"
msgstr "Možnosti aplikacije"

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--cache</option> <parameter>file</parameter>"
msgstr "<option>--cache</option> <parameter>file</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a cache file for the document."
msgstr "Ustvarite predpomnilniško datoteko za dokument."

#. Tag: option
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--check"
msgstr "--check"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the document for validity."
msgstr "Preverite veljavnost dokumenta."

#. Tag: screen
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The output can be a bit daunting, since one small mistake can cause a "
"cascade of errors. \n"
"The trick is to look at the first error, fix that error, save the file, and "
"run <command>meinproc6</command> again."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat je lahko nekoliko zastrašujoč, saj lahko ena majhna napaka povzroči "
"niz napak.\n"
"Trik je v tem, da pogledate prvo napako, jo popravite, shranite datoteko in "
"znova zaženete <command>meinproc6</command>."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<option>-o</option>, <option>--output</option><parameter> file</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<option>-o</option>, <option>--output</option><parameter> file</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output whole document to <parameter>file</parameter>."
msgstr "Izpis celotnega dokumenta v <parameter>datoteko</parameter>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "--stdout"
msgstr "--stdout"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output whole document to stdout."
msgstr "Izhod celotnega dokumenta v stdout."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--stylesheet</option> <parameter>xsl</parameter>"
msgstr "<option>--stylesheet</option> <parameter>xsl</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stylesheet to use."
msgstr "Slogovna tabela za uporabo."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--srcdir</option> <parameter>dir</parameter>"
msgstr "<option>--srcdir</option> <parameter>dir</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the root directory to look for kdoctools."
msgstr "Nastavite korenski imenik za iskanje kdoctools."

#. Tag: term
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>--param</option> key=value"
msgstr "<option>--param</option> key=value"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set parameters to pass to the stylesheet."
msgstr "Nastavite parametre za prenos v slogovno tabelo."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"Najpogostejši način za zagon <command>meinproc6</command> je preprosto kot "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout>, kjer je <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> običajno "
"index.docbook. Ta ukaz ustvari &HTML; strani iz datoteke DocBook. "
"Upoštevajte, da so te strani vidne samo v brskalnikih, ki temeljijo na &kde; "
"(kot je &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati &HTML; izpis v drugem brskalniku (na primer, če ga "
"postavljate na splet), uporabite <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> kjer je <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> polna "
"pot do enega od &XSL; slogovne tabele v &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. Za "
"izdelavo izhoda, primernega za splet, lahko uporabite <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> ali <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. Za več podrobnosti "
"glejte datoteko <filename>README</filename> v tem imeniku."

